        "text": "worthy of that and of that only, ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "the word being apparently substituted, after Jeremiah’s manner, for the technical word, not unlike in sound, which is translated “image work” in ",
        "children": []
      },
