        "text": ".",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "In the time of their visitation.—i.e., in the time when they are visited with punishment, as in 1Peter 2:12; Isaiah 10:3, and Luke 19:44.",
        "children": [
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "bld",
